Package org.tensorics.core.tensor

Interface Tensoric<V>

  • Type Parameters:
    V - the type of the values of the tensoric object
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    MappableTensor<V>, Scalar<V>, Tensor<E>, TensorView<V>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractScalar, AbstractTensor, BroadcastedTensorView, ImmutableDoubleArrayBackedTensor, ImmutableScalar, ImmutableTensor, ResamplingStage
    public interface Tensoric<V>
    The most generic interface of a multidimensional object within tensorics. Values can be retrieved from it and it knows for which positions it contains values.
